OL,3,CWelsh Water fined #1.35m for breaches
OL,4,Cof its permit to discharge sewage
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water has been fined
OL,7,F#1.35m after it plead guilty to more
OL,8,Fthan 800 breaches of its environmental
OL,9,Fpermits to discharge sewage.
OL,11,FThese were across 300 sites across
OL,12,FWales and Herefordshire.
OL,14,FThe charges relate to the self
OL,15,Fmonitoring data from the water company
OL,16,Fwhich it submitted to Natural
OL,17,FResources Wales (NRW) as part of its
OL,18,F2020 and 2021 annual reports.
