OL,3,CWelsh Water fined #1.35m for breaches
OL,4,Cof its permit to discharge sewage
OL,6,FSince 2010 there has been a
OL,7,Frequirement on water companies to
OL,8,Fcarry out self-monitoring of their
OL,9,Feffluent discharges from their sewage
OL,10,Fworks and water treatment works.
OL,12,FDwr Cymru says an internal restructure
OL,13,Fof the sampling team and IT-related
OL,14,Fscheduling issues along with the
OL,15,Feffects of the Covid-19 pandemic were
OL,16,Fthe main factors in the deterioration.
OL,18,FDue to the amount of non-compliances
OL,19,Frecorded, the charges were summarised
OL,20,Finto 18 offences by Dwr Cymru.
