OL,6,FHowever, even though the situation has
OL,7,Fsaid to have significantly improved by
OL,8,Fthe submission of the 2021 annual
OL,9,Freport, a number of non-compliances
OL,10,Fwere identified.
OL,12,FDue to the missing samples and data
OL,13,Ffrom the 2020 reporting year, it meant
OL,14,FNRW was unable to fully assess or
OL,15,Frespond to any environmental impacts.
