OL,6,FIn response a Welsh Water spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid:"Dwr Cymru Welsh Water has a
OL,8,Fstrong record of compliance with our
OL,9,Fmonitoring obligations prior to and
OL,10,Fafter the period relevant to this
OL,11,Fmatter.
OL,13,F"A combination of factors impacted our
OL,14,Fwork during 2020-21 that included the
OL,15,FCOVID 19 pandemic. Despite this we met
OL,16,Four monitoring requirements, which
OL,17,Finvolve more than 18,000 tests per
OL,18,Fyear, 98.95% of the time in 2020 and
OL,19,F99.45% in 2021.
