OL,3,CWelsh Water fined #1.35m for breaches
OL,4,Cof its permit to discharge sewage
OL,6,F"No sites were left unmonitored during
OL,7,Fthis time, but the unique
OL,8,Fcircumstances during 2020/21 caused
OL,9,Fsignificant challenges and disruption
OL,10,Fto our operations.
OL,12,F"There has been no identified
OL,13,Fenvironmental harm associated with
OL,14,Fthis case and the monitoring failures
OL,15,Frepresent a very small number of
OL,16,Fexamples in a programme involving tens
OL,17,Fof thousands of submissions each year.
OL,18,FNonetheless, we recognise that our
OL,19,Fcompliance fell short during 2020/21
OL,20,Fand we entered a guilty plea at the
OL,21,Fearliest opportunity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
