OL,4,Cof its permit to discharge sewage
OL,6,F"Welsh Water will continue to work
OL,7,Fclosely with our regulators to ensure
OL,8,Fthat we deliver on our two main
OL,9,Fpriorities, the best possible service
OL,10,Fto our customers and protecting the
OL,11,Fenvironment."
OL,13,FSian Williams, Head of Operations from
OL,14,FNatural Resources Wales said: "This
OL,15,Fcase highlights inadequacies in the
OL,16,Fprocesses at Dwr Cymru which led to
OL,17,Fwidespread permit breaches across
OL,18,FWales and over the border during a
OL,19,Fperiod of two years.
