OL,6,F"While we appreciate the disruption
OL,7,Fall businesses faced during 2020 with
OL,8,Fthe Covid-19 pandemic, we believe the
OL,9,Ffailings shown by Dwr Cymru were
OL,10,Favoidable should better contingency
OL,11,Fplanning have been in place.
OL,13,F"Dwr Cymru's performance has continued
OL,14,Fto decline for a number of years now,
OL,15,Fand this is a stark warning to the
OL,16,Fcompany that we will not hesitate to
OL,17,Fuse our enforcement powers to secure
OL,18,Fthe improvements we expect to see."
