OL,6,FNRW has downgraded Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,7,FWater from a four-star (industry
OL,8,Fleading) company in 2020 to two-star
OL,9,F(requires improvement) company in 2022
OL,10,Fand 2023 as part of its annual
OL,11,FEnvironmental Performance Assessment.
OL,13,FIn 2023, Dwr Cymru recorded it's worst
OL,14,Fperformance against environmental
OL,15,Fperformance metrics, with a spike in
OL,16,Fsignificant pollution incidents and a
OL,17,Fdecrease in incident self-reporting.
