OL,6,FMs Williams added: "The court's
OL,7,Fdecision is the culmination of this
OL,8,Fcomplex investigation into the
OL,9,Fcompany's performance across Wales and
OL,10,FHerefordshire. I'd like to pay tribute
OL,11,Fto the diligence and commitment of our
OL,12,Fregulatory teams in securing permit
OL,13,Fcompliance and enforcing the systemic
OL,14,Fchanges needed within the company.
OL,16,F"We will not hesitate to use our
OL,17,Fregulatory and enforcement powers
OL,18,Fwhere it is the appropriate thing to
OL,19,Fdo to bring any permit holder into
OL,20,Fcompliance.
